OL,3,CMan found dead at reservoir and woman
OL,4,Ctaken to hospital in Merthyr Tydfil
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a serious
OL,7,Fassault in Merthyr Tydfil, with a 36-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman taken to hospital and a
OL,9,F39-year-old man later found dead at a
OL,10,Freservoir.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police say the woman was
OL,13,Ftaken to the University Hospital of
OL,14,FWales from a residential address on
OL,15,FRocky Road in Merthyr Tydfil at around
OL,16,F11:50 pm on June 15.
OL,18,FThe 39-year old man was later been
OL,19,Ffound dead at Pontsticill Reservoir at
OL,20,F4.30am on June 16.
