OL,3,CMan found dead at reservoir and woman
OL,4,Ctaken to hospital in Merthyr Tydfil
OL,6,FForensic officers were seen outside
OL,7,Fthe Rocky Road address this morning.
OL,9,FPolice say next of kin have been made
OL,10,Faware and they are not looking for
OL,11,Fanyone else in connection with the
OL,12,Fincident.
